ExpressionVariable.Name: evActiveTi_TextColor
ExpressionVariable.ExpressionText: if $'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:LIO.OUT.Track' || $'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:LIO.OUT.Man' then 2 else if !$'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:LIO.OUT.Man' && !$'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:LIO.OUT.Track' && ($'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:FPIntPar.FP_PIDType' = 1 || $'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:FPIntPar.FP_PIDType' = 3) then 3 else 1

ExpressionVariable.Name: evActiveTd_TextColor
ExpressionVariable.ExpressionText: if $'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:LIO.OUT.Track' || $'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:LIO.OUT.Man' then 2 else if !$'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:LIO.OUT.Man' && !$'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:LIO.OUT.Track' && ($'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:FPIntPar.FP_PIDType' = 2 || $'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:FPIntPar.FP_PIDType' = 3) then 3 else 1

ExpressionVariable.Name: evApplyButton_Active
ExpressionVariable.ExpressionText: if !$'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:LIO.OUT.Track' && !$'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:LIO.OUT.Man' && !($'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:FPIntPar.FP_Gain' = $'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:Gain') || !($'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:FPIntPar.FP_Ti' = $'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:Ti') || !($'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:FPIntPar.FP_Td' = $'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:Td') then True else False

PropertyDescription.Name: Value
PropertyDescription.Value: if $'pr::PIDCtrl:Control Module:FPIntPar.FP_Dir' then Variant(False) else Variant(True)
